Date: Thu, 27 Mar 2025 20:10:52 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 3/8] wifi: ath12k: Move srng processing to wifi7 directory

Move ath12k_dp_service_srng API along with ath12k_dp_rx_process_reo_status
to wifi7 directory.
As srng processing is specific to atchitecture (wifi7 / wifi8),
the API ath12k_dp_service_srng is being moved to wifi7 directory.

The API which is invoked as part of service srng,
ath12k_dp_rx_process_reo_status is also moved to wifi7
directory, as the implementation is specfic to HW due to
the usage of wifi7 specific HAL macros.

Tested-on: QCN9274 hw2.0 PCI WLAN.WBE.1.3.1-00173-QCAHKSWPL_SILICONZ-1
Tested-on: WCN7850 hw2.0 PCI WLAN.HMT.1.0.c5-00481-QCAHMTSWPL_V1.0_V2.0_SILICONZ-3

Signed-off-by: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <quic_pnandesh@quicinc.com>
